### CZManager Agent API Tests
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension or similar

@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:17892
@token = ed96618839f2f2a2dad89649b733fce4

### Ping (public endpoint - returns token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/ping

### Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Scan all games
POST {{baseUrl}}/scan-games
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Search for specific game
POST {{baseUrl}}/scan-games
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "game_name": "Hogwarts"
}

### Search for GTA
POST {{baseUrl}}/scan-games
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "game_name": "Grand Theft Auto"
}

### Browse for folder (opens native dialog)
POST {{baseUrl}}/browse-folder
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Vyberte složku s hrou"
}

### Browse for file (opens native dialog)
POST {{baseUrl}}/browse-file
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Vyberte soubor",
  "filter": "*.exe"
}

### Get progress
GET {{baseUrl}}/progress
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get logs
GET {{baseUrl}}/logs
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get logs since index
GET {{baseUrl}}/logs?since=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Check for updates
GET {{baseUrl}}/update-check
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Install localization (example)
POST {{baseUrl}}/install
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "game_slug": "hogwarts-legacy",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "download_url": "https://example.com/localization.zip",
  "game_root": "D:\\Games\\Steam\\steamapps\\common\\Hogwarts Legacy"
}

### Uninstall localization (example)
POST {{baseUrl}}/uninstall
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "game_root": "D:\\Games\\Steam\\steamapps\\common\\Hogwarts Legacy"
}

### Cancel current operation
POST {{baseUrl}}/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
